          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Uber and Lyft coverage changes based on driver status: app off, waiting for request, or with passenger. Each phase has different limitsâ€”knowing which applies is crucial.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 card-hover">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary-100 text-primary-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Multiple Liable Parties</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Claims can involve the rideshare company, the driver, third-party drivers, and multiple insurance carriers. Our attorneys know how to navigate all parties.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 card-hover">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary-100 text-primary-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">$1 Million Policies</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            During active trips, Uber and Lyft carry $1M liability coverage. This means larger potential settlementsâ€”but insurance companies fight harder to deny claims.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Case Types -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Types of Rideshare Accident Cases We Handle
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Whether you were a passenger, driver, or hit by a rideshare vehicle, we connect you with attorneys who specialize in your type of case.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {featuredCases.map(caseType => (
          <a href={`/case-types/${caseType.slug}`} class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 card-hover border border-gray-100">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">{caseType.name}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4">{caseType.shortDescription}</p>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-primary-600 bg-primary-50 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
                {caseType.averageSettlement}
              </span>
              <span class="text-primary-500 font-medium text-sm">Learn More â†’</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <a href="/case-types" class="btn btn-secondary">
          View All Case Types
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- States Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Find Rideshare Accident Attorneys By State
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Laws and insurance requirements vary by state. Get connected with attorneys who understand your state's specific rideshare regulations.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {featuredStates.map(state => (
          <a href={`/states/${state.slug}`} class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 card-hover border border-gray-100">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">{state.name}</h3>
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 bg-gray-200 px-2 py-1 rounded">
                {state.abbreviation}
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-2 text-sm">
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="text-gray-500">Statute of Limitations:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">{state.statuteOfLimitations}</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="text-gray-500">Fault System:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">{state.faultSystem.split(' ')[0]}</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-between">
                <span class="text-gray-500">Avg. Settlement:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-primary-600">{state.averageSettlement.split(' - ')[0]}</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-200">
              <span class="text-primary-500 font-medium text-sm">View State Details â†’</span>
            </div>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <a href="/states" class="btn btn-secondary">
          View All 50 States
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 uber-gradient text-white">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">
          How Our Free Case Review Works
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Getting help for your rideshare accident case is simple and risk-free.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">1</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Submit Your Info</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">Fill out our quick form with basic accident details.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">2</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Free Consultation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">A rideshare accident attorney reviews your case.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">3</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Build Your Case</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">Your attorney handles negotiations with insurers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">4</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Get Compensated</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">Receive your settlement. No fees unless you win.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center mt-12">
        <a href="#free-case-review" class="btn btn-cta text-lg">
          Start Your Free Review Now
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Frequently Asked Questions
        </h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What insurance covers me as an Uber/Lyft passenger?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">As a passenger during an active trip, you're covered by Uber or Lyft's $1 million commercial liability policy. This applies regardless of who caused the accidentâ€”the rideshare driver or another vehicle.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">How much does it cost to hire a rideshare accident lawyer?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Our network attorneys work on contingencyâ€”you pay nothing upfront and no fees unless you win. The attorney fee typically comes from the settlement, usually 33-40%.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I sue Uber or Lyft directly?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">It's complicated. Uber and Lyft classify drivers as independent contractors, not employees. However, you can file claims against their insurance policies. An experienced attorney can help navigate this.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What if the Uber driver was at fault?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">If the rideshare driver caused the accident, their personal insurance and Uber/Lyft's commercial policy both may apply. The coverage depends on the driver's status in the app at the time of the crash.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">How long do I have to file a claim?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">This varies by stateâ€”statutes of limitations range from 1 to 6 years. However, evidence disappears and memories fade, so it's best to consult an attorney as soon as possible after your accident.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-primary-600 text-white">
    <div class="container-narrow text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
        Don't Let Insurance Companies Lowball You
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-primary-100 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Uber and Lyft's insurers are experienced at minimizing payouts. Get an attorney who knows how to fight for the compensation you deserve.
      </p>
      <a href="#free-case-review" class="btn bg-white text-primary-600 hover:bg-gray-100 font-bold px-8 py-4 text-lg shadow-lg">
        Get Your Free Case Evaluation
      </a>
      <p class="text-sm text-primary-200 mt-4">No fees unless you win. Available 24/7.</p>
    </div>
